high_descs: Turn left and go towards the wall, then left again to the fridge.
Take the silver bowl on the left from the fridge.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the bowl into the sink.
Go back to the fridge.
Take the second bowl from the fridge.
Go back to the sink.
Place the second bowl into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take two silver Bowl from a fridge and place them into a SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn left to walk to the fridge on the left.
Pick up the leftmost bowl from the fridge.
Turn around to face the larger sink.
Put the bowl in the sink.
Turn right to walk back to the fridge.
Take out the other bowl from the fridge.
Turn around to head back to the larger sink.
Put the other bowl on the right of the previous bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two Bowl in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Walk around the kitchen island to the fridge.
Remove the left most bowl from the top shelf of the fridge.
Walk to the left side of the sink.
Put the bowl down in the sink.
Walk back to the fridge.
Remove the bowl from the top shelf of the fridge.
Walk to the left side of the sink.
Put the bowl down in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two Bowl into the SinkBasin
